            <langmaterial id="ref37" label="Language of Materials note">Materials are in English</langmaterial>
            <abstract id="ref39" label="Abstract">This collection contains the files of The Brecht Forum, a Marxist cultural and educational center based in Brooklyn, New York. Founded in 1975 as the New York Marxist School, The Brecht Forum offers community based educational programs such as public lectures and seminars, art exhibitions, performances, popular education workshops, and language classes. Materials contained within this collection include Brecht Forum newspapers, event flyers, correspondence, photographs, programming files, minutes and reports from the New York Marxist School and Marxist Education Collective, and audio cassette recordings of conference events and lectures.</abstract>
        </did>
        <arrangement id="ref38">
            <head>Arrangement</head>
